          <msContents>
            <summary>Bull from Pope Pius III (formerly Francesco di Nanni Todeschini Piccolomini), dated Oct. 6, 1503. The bull is addressed to Silvio Piccolomini, a layman of Siena, appointing him an apostolic scribe. Pope Pius III's lead bull is attached to the document on a red and yellow silk string.</summary>
